title: #147:  The Persecution of Julian Assange With Graham Elwood
description:
Thank you for tuning in for another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode we welcome Graham Elwood to the show to discuss the life of Julian Assange and his prosecution by the US Government.

Please check out my new special "Zero Fucks" avail now on Vimeo.
